    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1993 Mazda RX-7 FD, featuring the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. This example maintains its factory-spec 50/50 weight distribution and remains mechanically pristine with verified high-compression numbers across all rotor faces. The chassis retains its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring razor-sharp lateral dynamics. Meticulously maintained with a refreshed vacuum line rack and a flawless cooling system. No aftermarket modifications; purely the raw, high-revving performance intended by Hiroshima\u2019s engineers. A true survivor for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
