    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute time-capsule specimen. This vehicle is in breathtaking condition, having been strictly garage-kept under a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with zero imperfections, scratches, or swirls, and is further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing or bolster wear, the dashboard is free of any UV damage, and even the original factory scent lingers. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been maintained exclusively by certified specialists with a comprehensive folder of records documenting every fluid change and multi-point inspection. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, with no signs of road debris, salt, or corrosion. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a truly preserved example. Sale includes all original manuals, two master keys, and the custom-fit breathable car cover.",
